---
import { SITE } from '../consts';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdSlot from '../components/ads/AdSlot.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description={`Terms of Service for ${SITE.name} — acceptable use, disclaimers and limitations of liability.`}
>
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 820px; padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem;">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>

    <section class="prose">
      <p>
        By accessing or using {SITE.name} (the “Service”), you agree to these Terms of Service. If you
        do not agree, please do not use the Service.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Use of the Service</h2>
      <p>
        The Service is provided for personal, non-commercial use. You may use our tools to perform
        calculations and conversions for your own purposes. You agree not to misuse the Service,
        attempt to disrupt it, or use it for any unlawful purpose.
      </p>

      <h2>2. No warranty</h2>
      <p>
        All tools are provided “as is” and “as available” without warranties of any kind. While we
        strive for accuracy, calculations are estimates for educational and planning purposes only.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Not professional advice</h2>
      <p>
        Our calculators and converters do <strong>not</strong> constitute financial, tax, legal,
        medical or professional advice. Always consult a qualified professional before making
        important decisions based on the results.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, {SITE.name} and its operators shall not be liable for
        any indirect, incidental or consequential damages arising from your use of, or inability to
        use, the Service.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        The software, design and content of the Service are owned by us or our licensors and are
        protected by applicable laws. You may not copy, redistribute or modify the Service without
        permission.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        The Service displays third-party advertisements (including Google AdSense). Advertiser
        content and practices are governed by the advertisers’ own policies.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may modify these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes
        acceptance of the updated Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction in which the Service operates,
        without regard to conflict-of-law principles.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms? Visit our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <AdSlot id="inContent" label="Advertisement" />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
